{"tid":1826053,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"羅拔唐尼《怪醫D老篤》評價惡劣","createTime":"2020-01-15T23:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T07:13:09.000Z","uid":41343,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"040aa4a83823828f28fc2c67d6539b8a3013cd3f","tid":1826053,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T23:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uFf7G4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuFf7G4G.jpg&h=ccc7f602&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://screencrush.com/the-funniest-dolittle-reviews/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscreencrush.com%2Fthe-funniest-dolittle-reviews%2F&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GNAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=910eef1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://screencrush.com/the-funniest-dolittle-reviews/</a><br />\n<br />\n影評摘要<br />\n<br />\nScreenCrush&rsquo;s film critic called Dolittle &ldquo;a cinematic Frankenstein&rsquo;s monster of poop jokes, fart jokes, itchy butt jokes, talking animals, wonky CGI, and Robert Downey Jr. going so big and broad he makes Johnny Depp&rsquo;s Captain Jack Sparrow look like an introvert.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nMichael Gingold, Birth.Movies.Death.:<br />\n<br />\nThe 1967 Doctor Dolittle was also a troubled, costly failure, so you could say this one is following in a classic tradition.<br />\n<br />\nRafer Guzman, Newsday:<br />\n<br />\n &lsquo;Dolittle&rsquo; has its moments, but those are few and far between. On the bright side, at least nobody tries to sing.<br />\n<br />\nGermain Lussier, io9:<br />\n<br />\nJust when I thought Dolittle couldn&rsquo;t get any less funny or idiotic, Robert Downey Jr. sticks his arms up a dragon&rsquo;s asshole. And I do mean that literally.<br />\n<br />\nHoai-Tran Bui, /Film:<br />\n<br />\nOne of the most perplexing twists from the film is that Banderas, who is 5 years older than Downey Jr., is playing his father-in-law. It&rsquo;s the equivalent of Russell Crowe calling Tom Cruise a young man in The Mummy.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHannah Lodge, The Beat:<br />\n<br />\nMaybe the animals could understand what Downey&rsquo;s Dolittle was saying, but I sure couldn&rsquo;t.<br />\n<br />\nDerek Smith, Slant:<br />\n<br />\nLike the CGI animals that inhabit much of the film, Dolittle is flashy and colorful on the outside but dead behind the eyes.<br />\n<br />\nRichard Roeper, Chicago Sun-Times:<br />\n<br />\nIf I could talk to the animals, I&rsquo;d say one thing: Please make it stop.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Arj017f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FArj017f.jpg&h=624a49c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a27af508b1a7be23a17aa3d34a36b4f36331815b","tid":1826053,"uid":149494,"like":15,"dislike":25,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T23:43:49.000Z","msg":"奧斯卡欠佢一個影帝"},{"pid":"d1f73df02985b378dd96afb35bfd851a9d24b9f1","tid":1826053,"uid":114217,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T23:46:15.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n劇本爛，唔關佢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a1843af22a046540576e14a2ec4ba0e5547b7f","tid":1826053,"uid":75050,"like":67,"dislike":2,"score":65,"quote":{"pid":"a27af508b1a7be23a17aa3d34a36b4f36331815b","tid":1826053,"uid":149494,"like":15,"dislike":25,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T23:43:49.000Z","msg":"奧斯卡欠佢一個影帝"},"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T00:02:08.000Z","msg":"佢扮黑人果套應該要比佢啦，笑到我仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/474x/45/02/45/4502458bf02f7ce040c64821c08a25a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2F474x%2F45%2F02%2F45%2F4502458bf02f7ce040c64821c08a25a4.jpg&h=c5a89abb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1e7c9176ddb0b4b4